}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== The ''[[Rosewill]]'' manual indicates the default SSID is ''Rosewill_XXXXXX'' :(or perhaps ''rosewill_XXXXXX'')
This device appears to be very similar to the [[TP-LINK TL-WR941ND v3.6]] :The OEM for this product is clearly ''[[TP-LINK]]'' / ''[[Proware]]''
From Rosewill's photos, the power adapter specs appear to be 9V and 0.85A (same as the [[TP-LINK TL-WR941ND v3.6]])
